We're here today asking for authority to convey a 50-foot wide access easement across three parcels of DOT-owned property, two of which were purchased with highway funds, one of which is rail property.

39
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:26,000
The reason we're asking for this is that back in the 70s, we had a well-intentioned project.

40
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:33,500
It was the Franklin Laconia Bypass, which we started acquiring property for at that time.

41
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:59,500
When we acquired property in this area, we ended up severing access to the parcel owned by JCB, who is the grantee in this case, LLC, we ended up severing access to that parcel back in 1978 when we purchased the property for the corridor for the bypass that I just mentioned.

42
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:08,000
